{"tid":415630,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"又黎on9制度【騰訊承諾退還未成年人不理性遊戲消費】","createTime":"2017-09-27T06:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T06:54:07.000Z","uid":20419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8acb876c50b4e89966ea1ab6bdb2ddb84d01ccb3","tid":415630,"uid":20419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T06:41:25.000Z","msg":"14:28 【騰訊承諾退還未成年人不理性遊戲消費】格隆匯27日訊，騰訊(<a href=\"http://00700.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00700.HK&d=B1ym5ZOO8g6sZ79udEQl19U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=4043bc63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00700.HK</a>)遊戲總監王磊表示，若接到不理性消費投訴，認定是未成年人行為，公司一律退還收費。王磊表示，部分孩子因為沉迷網絡遊戲，而認知度有限，經常被人利用，被誘導作不理性消費。騰訊作為全國最大網絡遊戲運營商，有責任和義務承擔部分責任。因此，騰訊會設立一條專線，通過快速的親子識別和消費核實，幫助家長把孩子的一些不理性、不健康的消費核實出來，只要認定是孩子的消費情況，會直接退還。（信報）<br />\n(來自格隆匯App港股財經快訊,點擊下載👉 <a href=\"http://dwz.cn/10dVck\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdwz.cn%2F10dVck&d=B1ym5ZOO8g6sZ79udEQl19U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=4faf8ef1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://dwz.cn/10dVck</a> )"},{"pid":"1c83776d99faa60d404f35d0415a2a4ef42f90a6","tid":415630,"uid":20419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T06:44:08.000Z","msg":"好低能"},{"pid":"896d85737cd5cc896d3cb158033a8138e6bfe53d","tid":415630,"uid":2404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T06:50:21.000Z","msg":"好事"},{"pid":"6da24829d5386e3769163abcdf1dd08a429e2712","tid":415630,"uid":75694,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T06:51:22.000Z","msg":"抽唔中就退錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59ab2c77d601fbc384de3f6273b16354ece98c1a","tid":415630,"uid":22054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T06:54:07.000Z","msg":"黨要佢做野，唔做抄家都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}